data.description: Escape to this Preinspected log cabin and ADU located on a fully fenced 5 acres of serene bliss. This 3 bed/2 bath home has the charm of vaulted ceilings, tons of natural light & gleaming hardwood floors throughout. Tons of storage in the attic above the master closet.  Home has new dishwasher, range, fridge, propane/electric stove, and 2 tankless water heaters. Home comes with new 8750-watt gas generator. Detached ADU has new paint, siding, updated electrical and flooring along with its own septic system, propane tank and washer/dryer hookups! Revel in the picturesque private country setting, adorned w/ fruit trees, a newly built 3/4 wrap-around deck & flourishing gardens. All of this and located only 30 minutes away from Olympia & Tacoma.
